Great Lakes Bar Control, Inc.
v.
Testa 2017-0655 Supreme Court of Ohio. July 18, 2018

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

On appellant's motion to reschedule oral argument before a master commissioner. Motion granted. The case is rescheduled for oral argument before a master commissioner on Tuesday, August 14, 2018.
